   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-a" image="QN_Npc_Velskud.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-b" mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>Where can I get such a thing?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>In order to purify something... You will need a substance that is <FONT color=#a82424>directly related connected to</FONT> the Black Dragon's powerful strength.<BR>Something that was attached to the Black Dragon would be ideal.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-b" image="QM_black_Dragon.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-c" mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>Hmm, will I have to use my bare hands for this?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>Didn't you see something like that with your own eyes the other time? I'm talking about the <FONT color=#a82424>Black Dragon's Broken Wings </FONT>.<BR>Bring that back so that it can be purified to prevent any more threats in Saint Haven... How does that sound? Isn't it a good idea?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-c" image="QM_black_Dragon.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-d" mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>Yes. I will try.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>This could be a fearful task but be brave. There shouldn't be a big problem from bringing just a part of it.<BR>As long as you make sure that you do not touch the Black Dragon's blood, it shouldn't cause a problem to such a hero like you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-d" image="QW_40.dds" itemindex="">
