      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>This dangerous energy...!<BR>It is emitting a light that is so bright, that even the Sage's eyes would fear it.<BR>There is no doubt that you have shown a glimpse of your mighty power, as you were able to bring it like this.</html>]]></talk_question>
